<taxonomicName authority="(Hedw.) Jenn." authorityName="Jenn." baseAuthorityName="Hedw." box="[1029,1355,1238,1262]" class="Bryopsida" family="Pottiaceae" genus="Tortella" kingdom="Plantae" order="Pottiales" pageId="8" pageNumber="841" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="species" species="humilis">
<emphasis box="[1029,1199,1238,1262]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="841">Tortella humilis</emphasis>
(Hedw.) Jenn.
</taxonomicName>
when it is sterile, but can be differentiated by having longer stems and non-fragile leaves. Habitat: rupicolous.
</paragraph>
